2. **Recall**: All target objects (tower cranes) should be localized by a bounding box. In the image, all visible tower cranes appear to be annotated with bounding boxes.

3. **Fit**: Each bounding box should neither be too loose nor too tight. The bounding boxes in the image seem to fit the tower cranes reasonably well, though some might be slightly loose, including parts of the construction site.
